<h2>AudioPal Instructions</h2>

<ol>
  <li>Visit the <a href="http://www.audiopal.com/" title="AudioPal - will open in a new window" target="_blank">AudioPal</a> site.</li>
  <li>Select &quot;Get Yours It's Free!&quot;</li>
  <li>Select to use your computer microphone (you will need to select &quot;allow&quot; for the site to access your mic). Note, there is also an option to call a toll-free phone number to record (this option requires you to input an access code that is provided).</li>
  <li>Select Record to start your message. Select Stop when you are done.</li>
  <li>Preview your recording to ensure it recorded properly.</li>
  <li>Provide your email address and select &quot;Get It!&quot;</li>
  <li>You will receive an email with a link to your recording (it is delivered quickly).</li>
  <li>Open the e-mail and select &quot;Click Here&quot; to publish your AudioPal.</li>
  <li>Copy the site URL, and paste the link into your assignment. </li>
</ol>
